track_notes:
Plenty of parking at Inverey, cycle to the abandoned  Altanour lodge and then start walking. Carn Bhac is first, then Beinn lutharn Mhor, Carn an Righ, Glas Tulaichean and finally An Socach. Return to bike and cycle back.

There are paths for quite a lot of the route but some sections you are just crossing heather and terrain, trying to avoid issues along the way -- peat hags, scree, rocks, minimising descent and ascent.

A long day!
track_title: Glen Ey 5 - A big day out
